posts.title: My First Post
posts.body: Candycode is an alternative agency that exclusively works with alternative people and companies to build avant-garde brands and cutting-edge websites. One of the founders, Sophia Andren, also runs the Tailwind Discord community. The candycode website is a Gatsby site and uses Tailwind CSS.
